PiFace version 0.01
===================

This is a Perl wrapper for PiFace's C library.
NOTE: the documentation of this library needs to be improved, and also we need tests. Feel free to contribute if you want to.
Please check PiFace.pm's perldoc (in lib/) for more details.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  A working C compiler (gcc)

  The following library (the C bindings): https://github.com/thomasmacpherson/piface

